title._content: Photograph of Chun Jan Yut with His Father Chun Duck Chin, 1899

description._content: Original Caption: "Chun Jan Yut, '7 years old,' with his father, Chun Duck Chin." This is one of four photographs of Chun Jan Yut taken at the ages of 1, 7, 14, and 22. From:: File Unit: Return Certificate Application Case File of Chinese Departing -- Chun Jan Yut (12017/2617), ca. 1892 - 1914 Created By:: Department of Justice.
